{"tid":680540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"200外傭遊行抗議容海恩歧視, 容海恩道歉","createTime":"2018-05-27T09:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T22:58:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"24497b7d2bafc2bc6818e6c0cc1f759bf3f7e7d3","tid":680540,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:12:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180527/s00001/1527398599787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180527%2Fs00001%2F1527398599787&d=GXNzoZh0xSHPFw8hkR3%2Bf8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0d4972bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180527%2Fs00001%2F1527398599787&h=21ea0101\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180527/s00001/1527398599787</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月27日 星期日<br />\n被指影響衛生　外傭組織遊行促容海恩道歉　容稱無意冒犯：抱歉 (13:43)<br />\n<br />\n新民黨立法會議員容海恩日前（23日）在立法會，批評外傭假日在公眾地方席地而坐、進餐及睡覺，影響公眾地方環境衛生。亞洲移居人士聯盟（AMCB）今日（27）上午11時在中環發起遊行至新民黨灣仔總部，要求容海恩就言論道歉。<br />\n<br />\n中午約12時許，容海恩接過團體請願信後向團體代表稱，其言論非有意冒犯外傭，但如外傭感到不受尊重（disrespectful），則感抱歉，並指本港正面對老年化問題，對外傭需求增加，會促請政府正視外傭假日休憩空間不足問題。容海恩原定中午12時正出席港台節目城市論譠，但因為接收請願信而遲到，她在論譠上提到，與外傭團體會面幾好，「交流得好好」。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲移居人士聯盟發言人Eman Villanueva表示，對容海恩願向團體代表表達歉意感到歡迎，但指並不足夠，認為容及新民黨應公開在傳媒及公眾面前就言論致歉。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍上午11時由中環遮打道出發至中午12時多到達新民黨灣仔總部附近，沿途高呼「我們是工人，不是奴隸」（We are worker, We are not slave）。警方發言人指，遊行約有二百人參加。<br />\n<br />\nEman Villanueva表示，本港有近38萬名外傭，平日工時長，不少人每日工作達16小時，一周工作6天，但只有一天休息，而假日則少有私人空間聚會，只好選擇在公眾地方休息，促請政府改善外傭工時長問題。"},{"pid":"4b962a2eebb1449f9b8bd3d932efc924abe9bdbc","tid":680540,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"from 01<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍接近12時遊行至新民黨總部附近的修頓遊樂場外，聯盟代表步行約3分鐘至新民黨總部，容海恩到樓下接信。容以英文向聯盟代表表示，早前言論令外傭感到不尊重「I&rsquo;m really sorry」，並指會為外傭要求政府提供更好設施及空間。"},{"pid":"eb00691e26fc524b8cf2bcf3498a19a315d32ee3","tid":680540,"uid":164913,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:14:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35022cb8fdfecd0da96d381a02c39b628aa69525","tid":680540,"uid":86841,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c22e23082feb4f6de787a73cddd4647e07e25e4","tid":680540,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ee8d010a460fd4b2bfa76c95114cd174d08c67","tid":680540,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"豬隊友"},{"pid":"d77847cf70ec3eac3e0080c8d6166991896f1df9","tid":680540,"uid":57705,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a397284aa09b9359edbe371375184e5e5f321e6a","tid":680540,"uid":15880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"DQ 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21922933eaba535d61086a1b0f7f4dee381a765","tid":680540,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6679d9abcf2edab9c666042e8f754b304b62e72","tid":680540,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"cls議員"},{"pid":"cc2da8fd1846963b082fe1d2ed1a1c2dacf44930","tid":680540,"uid":25676,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:28:15.000Z","msg":"其實佢又無講錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72933695e6713e3b69cb1601deca27579e598ad","tid":680540,"uid":33481,"like":1,"disl